author: Alec Leach
title: Nicki Minaj and Alicia Keys Dropped by Rick Owens’ FW17 Show in Paris
text:
Visit the original post to see all 25 images from this gallery. 
Location: Paris, France
Season: Fall/Winter 2017 Womenswear
Key Looks: Nicki Minaj killing it in some intergalactic Mykita sunglasses-slash-robot-visor combo — shame about the Balmain dress, though. Meanwhile, Alicia Keys is keeping it vibesy in #23.
Honored to sit w/this fashion queen #MichelleLamy while watching her husband's show. @rickowensonline 
A post shared by Nicki Minaj (@nickiminaj) on Mar 2, 2017 at 1:41pm PST 

Editor’s Notes: R&B megastars are into Rick Owens now? News to us. Anyway, the Lord of Darkness brought out all the fashion goths — just like he always does — for his FW17 women’s show in Paris . The mere mortals in attendance settled for just wearing head-to-toe Rick — naturally.
For more fashion week escapades, check out everything that went down at Off-White’s FW17 women’s show .
